Requirements
----------------------------------

* Python 2.7
* PyCrypto: https://www.dlitz.net/software/pycrypto/
* GCC: http://gcc.gnu.org/
* Boost Python: http://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_54_0/libs/python/doc/index.html
* Boost System: http://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_54_0/libs/system/doc/index.html
* gmpy: https://code.google.com/p/gmpy/
* openfst: http://www.openfst.org/


OS-specific hints:
----------------------------------

==== Ubuntu 12.04/12.10/13.04

$ sudo apt-get install libmpc-dev libmpfr-dev build-essential m4 python-dev python libboost-python-dev libboost-system-dev python-crypto python-gmpy python-scipy
$ cd src && make && make test

===== OSX 10.6+
* Install MacPorts: http://www.macports.org/
* Install XCode: https://developer.apple.com/xcode/

!! It is possible to build boost manually and use the OSX python.
!! However, it is much easier to use MacPorts to install all dependencies.

$ sudo port install py27
$ sudo port install boost -no_single
$ sudo port install py27-scipy
$ sudo port install py27-pip
$ sudo pip-2.7 install pycrypto
$ sudo pip-2.7 install gmpy

$ sudo pip install pycrypto
$ cd src && make && make test
